1139
01:35:58,882 --> 01:36:01,845
[GRUNTING]

1140
01:36:04,930 --> 01:36:07,891
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

1141
01:36:15,734 --> 01:36:17,402
[GROANING]

1142
01:36:20,447 --> 01:36:22,407
